Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:05.72,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向陽步道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:10.81,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}鹿撞愈疾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:17.94,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}散學廊下 鐘聲迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:21.34,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}無奇世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:25.75,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}漸始閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:32.47,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}走而出者 慕君之思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:38.48,opCbig5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}眼底心內 如系如縛
